Package: tutorizeR
Type: Package
Title: Convert R Markdown or Quarto Content into Interactive Tutorials
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person(
    given  = "AurÃ©lien",
    family = "Nicosia",
    email  = "aurelien.nicosia@mat.ulaval.ca",
    role   = c("aut", "cre")
  )
Description: Helps teachers convert existing '.Rmd' and '.qmd' teaching
    material into interactive tutorials for 'learnr' or 'quarto-live'.
    Conversion preserves narrative text, setup chunks, and major chunk
    options, supports teacher tags, and provides explicit validation and
    conversion reports.
